AD_MODULE.NAME: Openbravo V3
AD_MODULE.HELP: This modules is a template for 3.0 version of Openbravo ERP. The main goal of this release is to educate partners about this module and to receive as much feedback as possible from evaluators. All partners are encouraged to download and evaluate this module. Partners interested in deploying this module for new customers are recommended to thoroughly test their customer's business processes before deploying it into production environment. If you would like to help shape this module you are welcome to take part in the forum discussions or register feature requests or issues in the corresponding (Forum and Bug Tracking) sections in the Openbravo 3.0 template project in the OB Forge.
